    <forecast>
        <area aac="SA_FA001" description="South Australia" type="region">
            <forecast-period start-time-local="2026-05-30T21:18:25+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-30T21:18:25+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-30T11:48:25Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-30T11:48:25Z">
                <text type="warning_summary_footer">For latest warnings go to www.bom.gov.au, subscribe to RSS feeds, call 1300 659 210* or listen for warnings on relevant TV and radio broadcasts.</text>
                <text type="synoptic_situation">A cold front about the southeast moves into Victoria overnight. A weak high pressure system moves across from the west on Sunday. A significant low pressure system moves over waters to the south of SA on Monday and Tuesday reaching western Bass Strait Tuesday afternoon. A another low pressure moves over waters to the southeast on Wednesday. A high pressure system follows the low moving across northern parts of SA later in the week.</text>
                <text type="product_footer">* Calls to 1300 numbers cost around 27.5c incl. GST, higher from mobiles or public phones.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
        <area aac="SA_PW014" description="North East Pastoral" type="public-district" parent-aac="SA_FA001">
            <forecast-period index="0" start-time-local="2026-05-30T21:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-31T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-30T11:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-30T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Clear. Winds west to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-05-31T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-01T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-30T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-31T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Sunny. The chance of morning fog west of Leigh Creek. Winds southeast to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light in the middle of the day then becoming northwest to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 6 and 10 with daytime temperatures reaching between 17 and 23.</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 10:30am to 1:50pm, UV Index predicted to reach 4 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-06-01T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-02T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-31T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-01T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. High chance of showers south of Leigh Creek, near zero chance elsewhere. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late afternoon and evening. Damaging winds possible about the Gammon Ranges. Winds north to northeasterly 25 to 40 km/h increasing to 45 km/h before turning west to northwesterly 25 to 40 km/h during the day. Overnight temperatures falling to between 8 and 14 with daytime temperatures reaching 20 to 32.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-06-02T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-03T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-01T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-02T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. The chance of raised dust east of Leigh Creek in the morning. Medium chance of showers south of Yunta, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Near zero chance of rain elsewhere. The chance of a thunderstorm south of Yunta in the afternoon. Damaging winds possible about the Gammon Ranges. Winds westerly 30 to 45 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 12 and 17 with daytime temperatures reaching between 19 and 25.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-06-03T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-06-04T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-06-02T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-06-03T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny. Medium chance of showers south of Yunta, near zero chance elsewhere. Winds westerly 20 to 30 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 8 and 11 with daytime temperatures reaching between 18 and 23.</text>
            </forecast-period>
        </area>
